---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 課程介紹
---

<section class="space-y-6">
  <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold">慈心課程織圖</h1>
  <p class="text-stone-700">匯集課程結構、黑板畫、工作本、劇本、歌曲等素材，支援多課程瀏覽與站內搜尋。</p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    {% for c in coursesList %}
    <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-5">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2"><a class="hover:text-emerald-700" href="/courses/{{ c.slug }}/">{{ c.title }}</a></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 mb-3">{{ c.grade }}・{{ c.semester }}｜{{ c.unit }}｜{{ c.domain }}</p>
      <p class="mb-4 line-clamp-4">{{ c.overview or '' }}</p>
      <div class="flex gap-3 flex-wrap text-sm">
        <a class="pill" href="/courses/{{ c.slug }}/">課程主頁</a>
        <a class="pill" href="/courses/{{ c.slug }}/workbook/">工作本</a>
        <a class="pill" href="/courses/{{ c.slug }}/photos/">照片集</a>
        <a class="pill" href="/courses/{{ c.slug }}/blackboard/">黑板畫</a>
        <a class="pill" href="/courses/{{ c.slug }}/scripts/">劇本</a>
        <a class="pill" href="/courses/{{ c.slug }}/songs/">歌曲與音檔</a>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
